https://github.com/vuejs/vue-cli/tree/master

Installation
Prerequisites: Node.js (>=6.x, 8.x preferred), npm version 3+ and Git.

$ npm install -g vue-cli

Usage:
$ vue init <template-name> <project-name>
Example:
$ vue init webpack my-project

